  title="E-Bikes, are AWESOME!!"
  description=""
  category="Uncategorized"
  categorySlug="uncategorized"
>
<p>OMR has added E-biking to our growing list of fun things to shred the dirt, and let me tell you, it is FUN! If you&#8217;ve never tried one, now&#8217;s the time. The Specialized Levo is a full suspension rocket, that will shoot you up the steepest hill. You simply will be blown away at the performance. This is a full suspension mountain bike with a Bosch electric motor, that is active only when you are pedaling. From the rides I&#8217;ve taken, I estimate battery run time at @ 4 hours, with 50% steep climbs in the mix, or 30+ miles of trail. We&#8217;ve got a Medium frame which will fit 5&#8217;2&#8243; to 5&#8217;8&#8242;, and a Large frame for 5&#8217;9&#8242; and up. If you&#8217;re planning an extensive Moto trip, I highly recommend mixing the E-Bike into the workouts, every 3rd day for variety, and fun factor. Cheers!<img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2623" src="https://www.oregonmotorcyclerental.com/newsite/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/20170315_155848134-1-300x169.jpeg" alt="" width="300" height="169" srcset="../../wp-content/uploads/2017/04/20170315_155848134-1-300x169.jpeg 300w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2017/04/20170315_155848134-1-768x432.jpeg 768w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2017/04/20170315_155848134-1-1024x576.jpeg 1024w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2017/04/20170315_155848134-1-260x146.jpeg 260w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2017/04/20170315_155848134-1-50x28.jpeg 50w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2017/04/20170315_155848134-1-133x75.jpeg 133w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2017/04/20170315_155848134-1.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width:767px) 300px, 300px" /></p>
